# 3.1.1.research.external.q8.proactive-rotation

## question

how to detect limit approach before error? is there a quota API, or must we infer from rate limit response?

## options

- quota API exists (can check left)
- headers in response (X-RateLimit-Left style)
- no visibility (must wait for 429)
- usage API endpoint

## why it matters

proactive rotation (before limit hit) would be smoother than reactive (after 429).

## research approach

check anthropic api docs for rate limit headers, quota endpoints.

## note

may be out of scope for spike — reactive rotation acceptable for MVP.

## .status

awaited
